{"tid":1019754,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"大學生應徵者不自量力 真係不知所謂","createTime":"2019-02-13T06:57:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-13T11:14:16.000Z","uid":196627,"like":22,"dislike":514,"uniUserReply":62,"replies":[{"pid":"b6e4643454e0dc6c7f31def088dfc5cf5495af1b","tid":1019754,"uid":196627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T06:57:29.000Z","msg":"今日約左個Fresh Grad黎見工<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個大學生係xxu既(香港某知名大學)<br />\n聽講xxu既學生好勁架啦<br />\n咁佢地有幾「勁」呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n等我同大家分享先<br />\n<br />\n我:<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢:<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我﹕點解你想APPLY呢份工呀?<br />\n<br />\n佢: 因為我鐘意份工夠challenging，而我做事夠獨立，絕對係呢個POST既合適人選<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n(都答得幾求其喎)<br />\n<br />\n我: Simple question, simple answer。呢個係interview，唔係問書，唔好背之前既答案<br />\n<br />\n佢: SOR......SORRY(比我嚇疾左)<br />\n<br />\n我: 咁你有無internship經驗呀?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢: 我有呀，我起XXX(細公司)做過......<br />\n<br />\n我: 我見過既xxu學生都係起Goldman Sachs, Morgan Stanley做internship架喎。同佢地比，你間公司好似......<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢: ......(成塊臉紅晒)<br />\n<br />\n我: 咁你仲係咪好proud of 係xxu畢業呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢: 唔係......話好多名校graduate都會黎in 你地公司, 而且自己又唔係讀相關學科，所以冇咩特別優勢<br />\n<br />\n我:咁又係既，你果科收既分都幾低下，所以去internship都去得......<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/dllm.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢: ......(比我串到啞左)<br />\n<br />\n我: 其實好多xxu都好arrogant，以為自己係天之驕子，所以佢地都做得唔耐。但其實好多hku既畢業生都係無料扮四條咁<br />\n<br />\n佢: 聽你咁講，我覺得好surprised......<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我: surprised?!你之前冇research過既咩? 你咁樣邊夠有sincerity?<br />\n<br />\n佢: ......(好尷尬咁樣)<br />\n<br />\n我: 雖然你既質素無人地咁高，但係你都好arrogant喎，not humble enough。 你太self-centered啦, 一開始就覺得自己可以做好份工，又唔講我知你既weakness<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/wfc.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢: 咁我想做呢份工，我覺得being confident係好重要......<br />\n<br />\n我: 一個fresh grad 憑咩being confident? 憑你起XXX既經驗?好心你就humble d啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢: 自己其實唔係唔humble, 如果你想知我既weakness, 我可以詳細話你知......<br />\n<br />\n我: 太遲啦。你都係返去等消息啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n聽到我叫佢走之後<br />\n佢就頭dupdup<br />\n眼濕濕咁樣<br />\n然後垂頭喪氣咁執野走左啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n香港真係幾多呢D無料扮四條既大學生架"},{"pid":"da55d7f97c8cfe4866dd46c8fd0fe2f3c9f4b4e7","tid":1019754,"uid":78856,"like":223,"dislike":2,"score":221,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T06:57:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">樓主假膠 唔使理</span>"},{"pid":"c746890f13c07c75fb5dfea410431b84d2480386","tid":1019754,"uid":10277,"like":68,"dislike":4,"score":64,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T06:58:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PvbY6nv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPvbY6nv.png&h=49d0f56a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e83245967ecad523c8cfbca2c21533c589930ff4","tid":1019754,"uid":17765,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T06:59:38.000Z","msg":"你老母臭閪都又老又醜<br />\n又咪係企街做雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dc20d563a902cd36366196310d9200097eb62ba","tid":1019754,"uid":220701,"like":212,"dislike":1,"score":211,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T06:59:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D1AV8AW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD1AV8AW.jpg&h=01a73b37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"fon